{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"EventListener","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener_380cb5f366307beb2c072f74e561ee98","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>dispatchEvent()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>removeEventListener()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>EventListener</code></strong> 接口表示的对象可以处理 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> 对象所调度的事件。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> 由于需要与以前遗留的内容进行兼容，<code>EventListener</code> 可以接受一个函数，也可以接受带有 <code>handleEvent()</code> 函数属性的对象。这将在下面的<a href=\"#example\">例子</a>中展现出来。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>此接口未实现或继承任何属性。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>此接口未继承任何方法。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"eventlistener.handleevent\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventListener.handleEvent()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>一个在特定类型的事件被调用时运行的函数。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>点这里！<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> buttonElement <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'btn'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Add a handler for the 'click' event by providing a callback function.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Whenever the element is clicked, a pop-up with \"Element clicked!\" will</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// appear.</span>\nbuttonElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Element clicked through function!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 由于兼容性原因，一个带有 handleEvent 函数属性的对象也可以达到相同的效果。</span>\nbuttonElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">handleEvent</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Element clicked through handleEvent property!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例子\" id=\"frame_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener_380cb5f366307beb2c072f74e561ee98/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见：","title":"参见：","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\">addEventListener</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#callbackdef-eventlistener\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">EventListener</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>No change.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-EventListener\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">EventListener</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.EventListener","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener_380cb5f366307beb2c072f74e561ee98/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"EventListener 接口表示的对象可以处理 EventTarget 对象所调度的事件。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"EventListener","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/eventtarget/addeventlistener_380cb5f366307beb2c072f74e561ee98","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/eventtarget/addeventlistener_380cb5f366307beb2c072f74e561ee98/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conf